{"tid":135156,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【專家點睇】諾獎得主席勒：美股估值貴 減持啦喂！","createTime":"2017-02-26T06:48:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-27T11:30:35.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"53801fb210d6fe9f662b5f8eece1eabd86dfacdc","tid":135156,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T06:48:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/26/144642_e4ffbc45a8c9fd28ffcd2c1f5711894a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F26%2F144642_e4ffbc45a8c9fd28ffcd2c1f5711894a.jpg&h=18990b19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n諾貝爾經濟學獎得主席勒，籲減持美股。(路透社網站圖片)<br />\n<br />\n美股升勢凌厲，道指連續第11個交易日創新高。諾貝爾經濟學獎得主、耶魯大學經濟學教授席勒（Robert Shiller）籲減持美股。<br />\n<br />\n根據席勒創立的經周期調整市盈率（CAPE ratio）錄得28.66倍，為2002年以來最高，反映美股估值貴，而且達到令人憂慮水平，故建議投資者可減持美股。<br />\n<br />\n不過，席勒補充指股市短線波動較難預測，經周期調整市盈率升至高位，不一定反映股市將會出現股災，作為長線美股投資而言，回報表現有可能表現欠佳。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56352785&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56352785%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170225&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn22xr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=f4c2bc86\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56352785%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170225&h=14c403d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56352785&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170225</a><br />\n<br />\n//經濟學者講股票 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f157ca9752d8955b22e622841cda28446c4abe39","tid":135156,"uid":59099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T08:12:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/26/161229_cbe627491f46c